    Troy Ellison is an esteemed teacher a Regent International School in Dubai. He is the department lead of ICT and Computing, making worldwide headlines for his renowned teaching methods. He is a very respected individual in his field. Wikipedia
    Born: August 13, 1975 (age 50 years), Toronto, Canada
    Top Sudents: Billel Sekulic (dob. 2010), Niranjan Bobby (dob. 2009)
